 Popular Nollywood actress, Stephanie Okereke Linus has welcomed a bouncing baby with her husband, Linus Idahosa. Recall the couple had celebrated their 10th wedding anniversary a month ago with stunning images. Taking social media unawares, the 39 year old actress has taken to her Instagram page to announce the arrival of her bouncing baby boy. She wrote: “A Princely Arrival Glory be to His name. Stephanie & Linus”
Fans have taken to her comment section to congratulate the couple on the arrival of their child.